1
00:00:10,960 --> 00:00:13,420
♪The maple mark on your skin♪

2
00:00:14,230 --> 00:00:17,040
♪The only proof we exist♪

3
00:00:18,210 --> 00:00:21,450
♪I stole you back from destiny♪

4
00:00:21,560 --> 00:00:24,430
♪But can I redeem myself♪

5
00:00:24,430 --> 00:00:26,540
♪I don't care what fate foretells♪

6
00:00:26,750 --> 00:00:30,330
♪Or how rough the road may be♪

7
00:00:30,340 --> 00:00:33,280
♪Stay, I'll fight for you♪

8
00:00:33,610 --> 00:00:37,660
♪That's all I'll ever do♪

9
00:00:37,760 --> 00:00:39,890
♪If life is just a show♪

10
00:00:39,890 --> 00:00:42,650
♪I'll stay with you till the end♪

11
00:00:42,650 --> 00:00:44,980
♪I'm scared we'll wake up alone♪

12
00:00:44,980 --> 00:00:47,960
♪So don't let this dream end♪

13
00:00:47,960 --> 00:00:52,420
♪In my bones, in my heart♪

14
00:00:52,420 --> 00:00:54,100
♪I know I'll have to leave♪

15
00:00:54,100 --> 00:00:55,670
♪You must not leave my side♪

16
00:00:55,670 --> 00:00:57,260
♪No place can hold us in♪

17
00:00:57,260 --> 00:01:01,910
♪Not when it's you and me♪

18
00:01:06,890 --> 00:01:10,400
♪Forever♪

19
00:01:11,490 --> 00:01:15,250
♪In my soul♪

20
00:01:17,260 --> 00:01:23,300
=This Palace Maid Isn't Very Calm=
=Episode 13=

21
00:01:24,280 --> 00:01:25,680
What on earth happened?

22
00:01:26,230 --> 00:01:27,070
Just now,

23
00:01:27,080 --> 00:01:29,870
I saw His Majesty rush over.

24
00:01:29,870 --> 00:01:32,310
It seems something happened
at the training ground.

25
00:01:32,840 --> 00:01:34,480
Could something have happened
to the horse?

26
00:01:34,950 --> 00:01:36,230
I just saw the horse's body

27
00:01:36,230 --> 00:01:37,230
being carried out.

28
00:01:37,230 --> 00:01:38,230
It was covered in blood.

29
00:01:38,490 --> 00:01:39,790
What horse are you talking about?

30
00:01:39,790 --> 00:01:41,120
The 14th Prince had an accident.

31
00:01:41,840 --> 00:01:43,430
They said a wild horse slammed into him,

32
00:01:43,430 --> 00:01:44,560
and he was thrown from his mount.

33
00:01:44,560 --> 00:01:46,120
Both his legs are broken.

34
00:01:48,840 --> 00:01:50,000
How could this happen?

35
00:02:03,710 --> 00:02:04,590
How is my son?

36
00:02:06,790 --> 00:02:09,360
Your Majesty, the Prince is badly hurt.

37
00:02:09,560 --> 00:02:11,400
Luckily the bleeding
has stopped in time,

38
00:02:11,400 --> 00:02:13,400
so his life is not in danger.

39
00:02:13,800 --> 00:02:14,750
Then what about his legs?

40
00:02:15,470 --> 00:02:16,560
Are they seriously injured?

41
00:02:17,910 --> 00:02:19,150
Can he still stand?

42
00:02:19,590 --> 00:02:21,630
The leg bones are badly hurt.

43
00:02:21,810 --> 00:02:22,910
And his meridians are damaged.

44
00:02:23,150 --> 00:02:24,000
I'm afraid

45
00:02:24,030 --> 00:02:26,560
the Prince can't stand anytime soon.

46
00:02:26,870 --> 00:02:28,840
As for a full recovery later on,

47
00:02:29,080 --> 00:02:29,920
he will still need

48
00:02:30,120 --> 00:02:31,430
careful treatment.

49
00:02:32,590 --> 00:02:33,430
Mother!

50
00:02:34,800 --> 00:02:35,640
Physician Zhang,

51
00:02:35,870 --> 00:02:37,870
I order you to heal my brother.

52
00:02:38,150 --> 00:02:39,120
No matter what herbs you need,

53
00:02:39,120 --> 00:02:39,960
use them without hesitation.

54
00:02:40,400 --> 00:02:41,840
I understand.

55
00:02:48,630 --> 00:02:49,470
Your Majesty,

56
00:02:49,840 --> 00:02:50,870
the 14th Prince, he...

57
00:02:51,310 --> 00:02:52,150
Speak.

58
00:02:52,680 --> 00:02:53,870
What exactly happened?

59
00:02:54,100 --> 00:02:55,190
Please calm down, Your Majesty.

60
00:02:55,190 --> 00:02:56,630
The Prince went riding
at the horse ground.

61
00:02:56,800 --> 00:02:58,030
It was fine at first.

62
00:02:58,240 --> 00:02:59,280
But for some reason,

63
00:02:59,560 --> 00:03:01,590
the Prince's horse
got suddenly startled.

64
00:03:01,870 --> 00:03:04,630
In the end,
the Prince had to kill it to stop.

65
00:03:04,630 --> 00:03:06,080
But he was thrown off as well.

66
00:03:06,280 --> 00:03:07,430
A healthy horse.

67
00:03:08,160 --> 00:03:09,470
How could it be startled like that?

68
00:03:10,120 --> 00:03:10,960
Mother,

69
00:03:11,000 --> 00:03:12,280
I've ordered a full investigation.

70
00:03:12,840 --> 00:03:13,680
Mm.

71
00:03:14,360 --> 00:03:15,240
Your Majesty,

72
00:03:15,800 --> 00:03:17,680
how is the 14th Prince now?

73
00:03:19,960 --> 00:03:21,590
There was supposed to be a wedding.

74
00:03:22,000 --> 00:03:23,150
But now...

75
00:03:23,840 --> 00:03:25,360
14th Prince's leg.

76
00:03:28,910 --> 00:03:29,960
I'm afraid...

77
00:03:33,590 --> 00:03:34,630
No.

78
00:03:36,400 --> 00:03:39,030
The 14th Prince is such a proud man.

79
00:03:39,520 --> 00:03:41,120
How could he...

80
00:03:41,120 --> 00:03:42,520
That cannot be.

81
00:03:55,120 --> 00:03:55,960
Child,

82
00:03:56,630 --> 00:03:57,470
go back for now.

83
00:03:58,710 --> 00:04:00,630
When 14th Prince's legs heal,

84
00:04:01,000 --> 00:04:02,400
I'll call you back.

85
00:04:02,680 --> 00:04:03,520
Your Majesty.

86
00:04:08,470 --> 00:04:09,400
Yes.

87
00:04:31,040 --> 00:04:31,880
Be gentle.

88
00:04:35,430 --> 00:04:36,270
Gently.

89
00:04:39,430 --> 00:04:41,800
Your Highness, so you feel the pain now.

90
00:04:41,800 --> 00:04:43,630
I'm being as gentle as I can.

91
00:04:49,160 --> 00:04:50,000
Eunuch Fu,

92
00:04:50,070 --> 00:04:51,120
let me do it.

93
00:04:57,040 --> 00:04:58,070
If I'd known,

94
00:04:58,270 --> 00:05:00,120
I wouldn't have suggested this.

95
00:05:00,560 --> 00:05:02,000
You're hurt so badly.

96
00:05:02,460 --> 00:05:03,600
If it were not severe enough,

97
00:05:03,950 --> 00:05:05,920
how could I stop my mother's plans?

98
00:05:10,390 --> 00:05:11,240
Does it hurt?

99
00:05:11,240 --> 00:05:12,080
No.

100
00:05:13,800 --> 00:05:14,750
You're lying.

101
00:05:15,630 --> 00:05:18,360
Even a little scratch hurts me,

102
00:05:18,600 --> 00:05:20,120
let alone the state you're in now.

103
00:05:20,600 --> 00:05:22,040
Eunuch Fu, you'd better...

104
00:05:23,160 --> 00:05:24,270
It looks frightening,

105
00:05:24,630 --> 00:05:26,430
but I did this to myself.

106
00:05:26,430 --> 00:05:27,720
It hasn't broken the bone.

107
00:05:27,720 --> 00:05:28,830
But the Imperial Physician said...

108
00:05:28,830 --> 00:05:30,390
The Imperial Physician works for me.

109
00:05:30,720 --> 00:05:32,240
As long as the betrothal stands,

110
00:05:32,600 --> 00:05:33,560
my legs

111
00:05:34,160 --> 00:05:35,070
will never heal.

112
00:05:40,480 --> 00:05:41,680
You're so cruel

113
00:05:42,120 --> 00:05:43,830
to yourself.

114
00:05:44,510 --> 00:05:45,360
What?

115
00:05:45,680 --> 00:05:46,680
Are you worried about me?

116
00:05:48,240 --> 00:05:51,310
I'm afraid you'll blame me

117
00:05:51,310 --> 00:05:52,600
if your leg ends up crippled.

118
00:05:52,600 --> 00:05:53,510
I won't blame you,

119
00:05:53,750 --> 00:05:55,240
as long as you promise me one thing.

120
00:05:57,870 --> 00:05:58,750
Your Highness.

121
00:05:58,750 --> 00:06:00,120
What is it this time?

122
00:06:00,630 --> 00:06:02,240
You know my secret.

123
00:06:02,830 --> 00:06:03,720
Why not

124
00:06:04,120 --> 00:06:05,830
stay and serve me

125
00:06:06,040 --> 00:06:07,680
and keep this secret with me?

126
00:06:08,360 --> 00:06:09,200
I...

127
00:06:20,830 --> 00:06:22,800
14th Prince asked me to

128
00:06:23,480 --> 00:06:25,240
keep you by his side.

129
00:06:25,430 --> 00:06:27,430
You used to serve me.

130
00:06:27,720 --> 00:06:29,270
And you have always known your place.

131
00:06:29,310 --> 00:06:32,480
I mean to grant you
the official title of Lady.

132
00:06:32,800 --> 00:06:34,720
Just stay by 14th Prince's side,

133
00:06:34,720 --> 00:06:36,270
and take good care of him.

134
00:06:39,310 --> 00:06:40,510
Your Majesty,

135
00:06:40,510 --> 00:06:41,720
I don't want a title.

136
00:06:42,190 --> 00:06:45,390
I'm willing to serve the 14th Prince
as a physician.

137
00:06:45,720 --> 00:06:47,870
Do you think the title is too low?

138
00:06:48,560 --> 00:06:50,240
No, I dare not.

139
00:06:50,750 --> 00:06:53,720
It is only that
I'm from a humble family.

140
00:06:54,410 --> 00:06:56,000
So I'm not good enough
for the 14th Prince.

141
00:06:56,510 --> 00:06:59,310
I never wanted a title I don't deserve.

142
00:06:59,480 --> 00:07:00,680
I only want to

143
00:07:00,680 --> 00:07:02,800
serve you and the Prince.

144
00:07:02,800 --> 00:07:05,720
Repay your kindness.

145
00:07:06,190 --> 00:07:07,630
You have served me for a long time.

146
00:07:08,040 --> 00:07:10,830
I'm not one to forget old ties.

147
00:07:10,870 --> 00:07:12,270
I know

148
00:07:12,270 --> 00:07:14,920
the title of Lady is somewhat low.

149
00:07:15,600 --> 00:07:17,390
But if you serve him well,

150
00:07:17,720 --> 00:07:19,360
once 14th Prince is married,

151
00:07:19,360 --> 00:07:21,950
I will see you wed from the Palace

152
00:07:22,270 --> 00:07:24,270
in grand style.

153
00:07:24,390 --> 00:07:26,920
Then, if you bear him a child or two,

154
00:07:27,100 --> 00:07:28,720
granting you
the title of Secondary Consort

155
00:07:28,840 --> 00:07:30,070
wouldn't be hard.

156
00:07:30,740 --> 00:07:31,750
Thank you for your grace.

157
00:07:31,950 --> 00:07:33,040
I appreciate it.

158
00:07:33,870 --> 00:07:35,800
But I'm a physician,

159
00:07:35,900 --> 00:07:36,950
so I want to heal people and

160
00:07:37,300 --> 00:07:39,120
I don't wish to be confined
to the inner household.

161
00:07:39,600 --> 00:07:42,600
Nor would I trade my true self
for mere official status.

162
00:07:43,120 --> 00:07:46,240
As long as I can serve the 14th Prince,

163
00:07:46,390 --> 00:07:48,310
and treat his illness,

164
00:07:48,600 --> 00:07:50,680
it's already my greatest blessing.

165
00:07:54,360 --> 00:07:55,200
Mother,

166
00:07:56,120 --> 00:07:58,120
let's put the title aside.

167
00:07:59,270 --> 00:08:00,110
I

168
00:08:00,720 --> 00:08:02,680
have something important to discuss.

169
00:08:02,680 --> 00:08:04,040
What else is it?

170
00:08:04,630 --> 00:08:05,800
I...

171
00:08:07,800 --> 00:08:08,720
I take my leave.

172
00:08:08,920 --> 00:08:09,760
Mm.

173
00:08:11,070 --> 00:08:12,920
Just as Physician Zhang said,

174
00:08:13,510 --> 00:08:14,680
my legs

175
00:08:14,870 --> 00:08:16,270
will take at least a year

176
00:08:16,270 --> 00:08:17,430
to heal.

177
00:08:17,430 --> 00:08:18,480
Even if they heal,

178
00:08:18,480 --> 00:08:19,920
I'll be lame.

179
00:08:19,920 --> 00:08:21,070
Full recovery

180
00:08:21,630 --> 00:08:22,680
is nowhere in sight.

181
00:08:22,870 --> 00:08:24,070
As for your leg injury,

182
00:08:24,070 --> 00:08:26,070
take your time and heal.
There's no rush.

183
00:08:26,510 --> 00:08:27,600
What matters most is

184
00:08:27,750 --> 00:08:29,310
not to be disabled.

185
00:08:29,310 --> 00:08:30,240
Mother,

186
00:08:30,560 --> 00:08:31,750
but some things

187
00:08:32,120 --> 00:08:33,240
can't wait.

188
00:08:33,390 --> 00:08:34,790
What do you mean?

189
00:08:35,320 --> 00:08:36,510
Tongjia Baozhu

190
00:08:36,510 --> 00:08:37,910
has reached her marriageable age.

191
00:08:38,270 --> 00:08:39,200
I

192
00:08:40,120 --> 00:08:41,320
am now crippled.

193
00:08:42,030 --> 00:08:43,670
I don't want to delay her future.

194
00:08:44,120 --> 00:08:45,390
Mother, please

195
00:08:45,390 --> 00:08:46,630
cancel the engagement.

196
00:08:47,120 --> 00:08:48,600
You only hurt your legs.

197
00:08:48,720 --> 00:08:49,600
You're not useless.

198
00:08:49,910 --> 00:08:51,600
You carry the royal bloodline.

199
00:08:51,600 --> 00:08:53,120
Even if you truly end up lame,

200
00:08:53,120 --> 00:08:55,630
someone will still marry you.

201
00:08:56,000 --> 00:08:59,120
Tongjia Baozhu
is just a general's daughter.

202
00:08:59,360 --> 00:09:00,320
Marrying you

203
00:09:00,630 --> 00:09:02,120
is her honor.

204
00:09:02,390 --> 00:09:03,360
Mother,

205
00:09:03,630 --> 00:09:06,150
the General of Martial Might
is a haughty man.

206
00:09:06,600 --> 00:09:07,480
I

207
00:09:07,480 --> 00:09:08,750
have no power or title.

208
00:09:09,670 --> 00:09:10,870
And I'm disabled.

209
00:09:11,440 --> 00:09:13,240
In his heart, he must be unwilling.

210
00:09:13,240 --> 00:09:16,080
Besides, marriage concerns two people.

211
00:09:16,360 --> 00:09:17,870
A forced marriage

212
00:09:19,030 --> 00:09:19,870
is futile.

213
00:09:20,360 --> 00:09:21,750
Sounds like

214
00:09:22,120 --> 00:09:24,080
you already have a plan.

215
00:09:25,030 --> 00:09:26,750
You must understand this marriage

216
00:09:26,750 --> 00:09:29,200
was carefully chosen by me.

217
00:09:29,790 --> 00:09:31,440
It will greatly benefit you.

218
00:09:31,960 --> 00:09:34,200
Tongjia Baozhu loves you deeply.

219
00:09:34,740 --> 00:09:36,390
The General of Martial Might's family

220
00:09:36,390 --> 00:09:37,720
is thriving.

221
00:09:38,030 --> 00:09:40,440
If one day I pass away,

222
00:09:41,150 --> 00:09:43,960
you will still have
your wife's family to rely on.

223
00:09:44,200 --> 00:09:46,600
Mother, don't say that.

224
00:09:48,360 --> 00:09:51,000
I understand what you mean,

225
00:09:51,480 --> 00:09:53,270
but I am grown now.

226
00:09:53,270 --> 00:09:54,390
I want to choose

227
00:09:54,670 --> 00:09:55,960
my own life.

228
00:10:02,630 --> 00:10:03,470
Coming.

229
00:10:03,770 --> 00:10:04,630
My Lady,

230
00:10:04,630 --> 00:10:06,630
His Majesty is taking this route today.

231
00:10:06,630 --> 00:10:08,480
The imperial procession
will be here any moment.

232
00:10:08,480 --> 00:10:09,320
Really?

233
00:10:09,790 --> 00:10:10,870
That's wonderful.

234
00:10:11,270 --> 00:10:13,790
Then the reward you promised me...

235
00:10:16,200 --> 00:10:17,840
Take this for now.

236
00:10:19,600 --> 00:10:20,910
J... just this little?

237
00:10:20,910 --> 00:10:21,760
My Lady,

238
00:10:21,790 --> 00:10:22,720
this is a bit...

239
00:10:23,550 --> 00:10:25,390
This is all I have.

240
00:10:25,870 --> 00:10:26,870
Once I win favor,

241
00:10:27,200 --> 00:10:28,390
I'll reward you generously.

242
00:10:32,270 --> 00:10:34,440
I can only help you this far.

243
00:10:56,510 --> 00:10:57,360
Your Majesty,

244
00:10:57,630 --> 00:10:59,390
should I send someone to check

245
00:10:59,670 --> 00:11:00,960
who is dancing over there?

246
00:11:01,360 --> 00:11:02,200
No need.

247
00:11:03,080 --> 00:11:04,600
I'll go see myself.

248
00:11:07,910 --> 00:11:08,750
Alright.

249
00:11:09,270 --> 00:11:10,270
Just now,

250
00:11:10,910 --> 00:11:12,150
what the Empress Dowager said

251
00:11:12,150 --> 00:11:13,440
was not my wish.

252
00:11:13,870 --> 00:11:14,720
I know.

253
00:11:14,720 --> 00:11:16,750
We're just acting.

254
00:11:17,270 --> 00:11:18,550
Please rest easy, Your Highness.

255
00:11:18,550 --> 00:11:20,000
I won't take it seriously.

256
00:11:20,000 --> 00:11:21,510
You think everything I do

257
00:11:23,550 --> 00:11:24,630
is just an act?

258
00:11:26,480 --> 00:11:27,320
Isn't it?

259
00:11:27,630 --> 00:11:28,720
Not just you, Your Highness.

260
00:11:28,720 --> 00:11:29,720
I'm acting as well.

261
00:11:29,720 --> 00:11:32,360
You play the loyal prince.

262
00:11:32,600 --> 00:11:34,870
And I play the dutiful physician.

263
00:11:35,080 --> 00:11:36,080
We both know the truth.

264
00:11:36,080 --> 00:11:36,920
It's mutually beneficial.

265
00:11:36,920 --> 00:11:37,960
No need to be serious.

266
00:11:37,960 --> 00:11:39,360
What if I said

267
00:11:39,630 --> 00:11:41,240
I truly want to

268
00:11:41,240 --> 00:11:42,630
give you a title?

269
00:11:44,550 --> 00:11:45,390
Don't.

270
00:11:45,400 --> 00:11:46,750
That is far too unsettling.

271
00:11:47,080 --> 00:11:50,150
Besides, I could never
live only for a husband.

272
00:11:50,150 --> 00:11:51,030
Nor will I

273
00:11:51,030 --> 00:11:53,320
share one husband with other women.

274
00:11:53,630 --> 00:11:55,910
And I have skills of my own.

275
00:11:55,910 --> 00:11:57,720
I can go anywhere.

276
00:11:57,720 --> 00:11:59,240
Why should I trap myself?

277
00:11:59,550 --> 00:12:00,960
What's more,

278
00:12:01,960 --> 00:12:03,240
back in my hometown,

279
00:12:03,720 --> 00:12:05,320
there is already someone I love.

280
00:12:07,360 --> 00:12:08,480
I take my leave.

281
00:12:22,670 --> 00:12:25,030
Sister, your chambers are truly grand.

282
00:12:26,240 --> 00:12:27,510
These ornaments here

283
00:12:27,510 --> 00:12:29,750
are all tributes from
the Imperial Household, aren't they?

284
00:12:31,360 --> 00:12:34,320
Miss Xiao,
you became a Noble Lady after one night.

285
00:12:34,750 --> 00:12:35,600
It seems

286
00:12:35,800 --> 00:12:38,120
His Majesty truly cares for you.

287
00:12:38,240 --> 00:12:39,080
Noble Lady,

288
00:12:39,080 --> 00:12:41,360
these are all flowers
His Majesty had sent over.

289
00:12:42,080 --> 00:12:44,550
Today, thanks to His Majesty's favor,

290
00:12:44,910 --> 00:12:47,320
he sent someone to deliver the flowers.

291
00:12:48,240 --> 00:12:50,600
Why are there flowers from all seasons?

292
00:12:50,700 --> 00:12:52,630
I heard the Imperial Garden
has a heated pavilion.

293
00:12:52,630 --> 00:12:55,200
Flowers of any season
can be grown there.

294
00:12:55,440 --> 00:12:57,270
Even so, these flowers are far too rare

295
00:12:57,270 --> 00:12:58,510
and very hard to get.

296
00:12:59,240 --> 00:13:01,270
You're so favored.

297
00:13:01,270 --> 00:13:02,510
I'm so jealous.

298
00:13:04,670 --> 00:13:07,150
Too bad there are no peonies.

299
00:13:09,000 --> 00:13:10,390
What do you mean?

300
00:13:12,480 --> 00:13:14,670
You're as beautiful as a peony.

301
00:13:14,750 --> 00:13:15,960
Among all the flowers,

302
00:13:15,960 --> 00:13:18,120
only peony is worthy of you.

303
00:13:19,000 --> 00:13:21,840
But peony is delicate.

304
00:13:22,480 --> 00:13:25,080
I hear only the most favored concubines

305
00:13:25,080 --> 00:13:27,440
receive peony bestowed by His Majesty.

306
00:13:31,000 --> 00:13:32,870
I just said it casually.

307
00:13:32,870 --> 00:13:34,000
Forgive me.

308
00:13:36,270 --> 00:13:38,080
So you mean I'm not favored enough?

309
00:13:38,670 --> 00:13:40,000
Don't overthink.

310
00:13:40,000 --> 00:13:41,120
I didn't mean that.

311
00:13:42,390 --> 00:13:43,360
It's just a peony.

312
00:13:43,870 --> 00:13:44,910
If I want it,

313
00:13:45,630 --> 00:13:46,600
I need only ask tomorrow,

314
00:13:47,150 --> 00:13:49,200
and His Majesty
will send it to me himself.

315
00:13:55,550 --> 00:13:57,990
♪I am but an outsider♪

316
00:13:58,030 --> 00:14:00,190
♪Yet something drags me deeper♪

317
00:14:00,430 --> 00:14:04,470
♪Outwit the world
but not the way we meet♪

318
00:14:04,470 --> 00:14:08,710
♪Splendid blooms line deadly ground♪

319
00:14:12,990 --> 00:14:16,230
♪Life's a phantom, yet I find you♪

320
00:14:16,390 --> 00:14:19,790
♪In a world of lies,
you're all that's clear♪

321
00:14:19,790 --> 00:14:22,310
♪I know how this story ends♪

322
00:14:22,310 --> 00:14:26,870
♪I still want what's in your eyes♪

323
00:14:27,190 --> 00:14:31,310
♪Truth or lie—I can't tell♪

324
00:14:36,270 --> 00:14:39,590
♪You hide it all behind your lines♪

325
00:14:39,590 --> 00:14:42,870
♪So familiar, yet out of reach♪

326
00:14:43,070 --> 00:14:46,150
♪A history that no one can search♪

327
00:14:46,390 --> 00:14:49,670
♪Like you drift in from another star♪

328
00:14:49,710 --> 00:14:51,470
♪I am but an outsider♪

329
00:14:51,470 --> 00:14:53,710
♪Yet something drags me deeper♪

330
00:14:53,710 --> 00:14:57,750
♪Outwit the world
but not the way we meet♪

331
00:14:57,750 --> 00:15:02,430
♪Splendid blooms line deadly ground♪

332
00:15:06,350 --> 00:15:09,750
♪Life's a phantom, yet I find you♪

333
00:15:09,750 --> 00:15:13,110
♪In a world of lies,
you're all that's clear♪

334
00:15:13,110 --> 00:15:15,590
♪I know how this story ends♪

335
00:15:15,590 --> 00:15:19,750
♪I still want what's in your eyes♪

336
00:15:19,750 --> 00:15:23,030
♪When it's over and I'm gone♪

337
00:15:23,030 --> 00:15:26,830
♪Please forget me and move on♪

338
00:15:26,830 --> 00:15:33,070
♪Just let this absurd dream fade♪

339
00:15:36,230 --> 00:15:44,590
♪Snow hides our tracks♪

340
00:15:48,150 --> 00:15:57,870
♪When do I finally wake♪
